Detailed Description

cvmx_srio::_int2_enable

SRIO_INT2_ENABLE = SRIO Interrupt 2 Enable

Allows SRIO to generate additional interrupts when corresponding enable bit is set.

Notes: This register enables interrupts in SRIO(0,2..3)_INT2_REG that can be asserted while the MAC is in reset. The register can be accessed/modified regardless of the value of SRIO(0,2..3)_STATUS_REG.ACCESS.

Clk_Rst: SRIO(0,2..3)_INT2_ENABLE sclk srst_n
